OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779711071
OL,3,C23-year-old Devon man killed in action
OL,4,Cin Ukraine
OL,6,FA 23-year-old man from Devon has been
OL,7,Fkilled in Ukraine.
OL,9,FAyrton Redfearn died in the Donetsk
OL,10,Fregion on May 9 whilst supporting the
OL,11,FUkrainian army.
OL,13,FAyrton attended Churston Ferrers
OL,14,FGrammar School and joined 200 Squadron
OL,15,FTorquay Air Cadets at 12 years old.
OL,17,FAt 17, he enlisted in the Royal Air
OL,18,FForce, where he trained as a Regiment
OL,19,FGunner and became a Senior Aircraftman
OL,20,F(SAC).
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
