OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779711071
OL,3,C23-year-old Devon man killed in action
OL,4,Cin Ukraine
OL,6,FLast year he joined a specialist
OL,7,Fmilitary unit for ex overseas military
OL,8,Fpersonnel, attached to the Army of
OL,9,FUkraine.
OL,11,FHis mother, Natasha paid tribute to
OL,12,Fher 'beautiful, brave son'. She said
OL,13,Fhe was 'extremely happy in Ukraine'
OL,14,Fand made 'exceptional' friends from
OL,15,Faround the world.
OL,17,FIn a statement she explained how
OL,18,FAyrton was due to receive his first
OL,19,Fbravery award for saving someone's
OL,20,Flife just five days after he died in
OL,21,Faction.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
