OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1779711071
OL,3,C23-year-old Devon man killed in action
OL,4,Cin Ukraine
OL,6,FNatasha and Ayrton's younger brother
OL,7,Fsay they are finding comfort in
OL,8,Fknowing he died a hero.
OL,10,FOthers have praised him for his
OL,11,F'exceptional service' and remembering
OL,12,Fhim for being a 'clever, funny,
OL,13,Fprankster whilst off duty, always able
OL,14,Fto boost morale.'
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Foreign,
OL,17,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,18,F(FCDO) said: "We are supporting the
OL,19,Ffamily of a British national who has
OL,20,Fdied in Ukraine, and are in contact
OL,21,Fwith the Ukrainian authorities".
